No. 09-10876. Donald Bullcoming, Petitioner v. New Mexico. 561 U.S. 1058, 131 S. Ct. 62,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1152,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5754. September 28, 2010.

Same case below, 147 N.M. 487, 226 P.3d 1.
